text: Eesti Telefilm is an Estonian movie studio established in 1956. It is structural unit of Eesti Televisioon.EE 12. köide, 2003: 104. The studio is produced documentary and live action films. ==Filmography (selection)== *1969 Mehed ei nuta *1972 A Young Retiree *1979 Siin me oleme! *1998 Georgica == References == Category:Film production companies of Estonia Category:Companies established in 1956 Category:1956 establishments in Estonia Category:Mass media in Estonia Category:Mass media companies established in 1956
